    "en": {
      "title": "A-level practical tests for three days from tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The examination department states that the candidates who could not participate in the practical tests of the General Certificate of Education A Level - 2021 examination will start from tomorrow (19) to 21.",
        "The practical tests of the subject of Western Music will be held tomorrow at the Battaramulla Examination Department.",
        "Practical tests in the subjects of Native Dance, Indian Dance, Home Economics, Oriental Music, Carnatic Music, Drama and Drama (Sinhala) and Drama and Drama (Tamil) will be held on tomorrow (20).",
        "Practical tests of Engineering Technology and Biosystems Technology will be held tomorrow (21)."
      ],
